       <header>
      <h2>How it Works</h2>
      <p class="10u -1u">
        CLC matches students who speak two different languages, each learning the other’s language.  Students then meet up informally to practice speaking their foreign language with each other.  Users fill out an online profile and are matched with a partner based on language and interests.  
      </p>
        </header>
